text: Rockabilly Baby is a 1957 American musical movie directed by William F. Claxton and starring Virginia Field, Douglas Kennedy, Irene Ryan, Ellen Corby, Frank Sully, Marlene Willis. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1957 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:Movies directed by William F. Claxton
